                <h1>Beyond the arc: Allen, Trent lead the way for the Blue Devils against the Irish</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/78de5e3b-7062-4edd-9d6c-8965824c062d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Grayson&#x20;Allen&#x20;led&#x20;the&#x20;Blue&#x20;Devils&#x20;backcourt&#x20;after&#x20;a&#x20;quiet&#x20;outing&#x20;against&#x20;Virginia&#x20;Saturday.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
